data.text:
published on 2019-06-24T17:58:46Z

Maija excited about her return to comedy & NYC, flashes us back to why she left NYC to LA for Hollywood in the first place. The Adventures of Comedian Maija Di Giorgio who returns to comedy in NYC with parody flashbacks to where she has been as a comedian, filmmaker and radio host from NYC to LA and more! With her BFF Producer Heather McConnell. Narrated by Comedian Jeff Husbands.

Genre

Comedy
